
Create a popup that floats in top 5px of content.

```
.container {
    position: relative;
}
.popup {
    position: absolute !important;
    display: block;
    z-index: 100;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    bottom: 5px;
}
```

```
<div class='container'>
    <div class='popup'>Popup text here</div>
    <div class='content'>Contents here</div>
</div>
```